  <h2>QR Encoding</h2>
  <p>We make QR codes rugged:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Encode manifest SHA-256 as base32 with a version prefix.</li>
    <li>Use QR error-correction (M or Q) to handle glare and dust.</li>
    <li>Add a tamper stripe sticker for enclosure panels.</li>
  </ul>

